custom-meta.meta-value: Data relating to catch and effort in the South Australian Rock Lobster Fishery are confidential and available from the South Australian Research and Development Institute (contact via Angelo Tsolos; angelo.tsolos@sa.gov.au) for researchers who meet the criteria for access to confidential data. Climatological data are available through the Integrated Marine Observing System (IMOS) through the Australian Ocean Data Network ( https://portal.aodn.org.au/) and IMOS Ocean Current website ( oceancurrent.imos.org.au/product).
